cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.CV

The paper deals with dimensionality reduction techniques and their application in machine learning tasks such as matrix multiplication, linear regression, and classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves statistical analysis and information theory, which suggests the possibility of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory) categories. The use of RP in classification and regression tasks also indicates the possibility of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) category. Finally, the paper includes experiments with image data, which suggests the possibility of cs.CV (Computer Vision) category.
